AKB48在《[[Coming_Soon!!|Coming Soon!!]]》<ref>{{ja icon}}{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/music/news/58448 |title=来週カミスン！にAKB48、A.N.JELL、若旦那、稲垣潤一ら |publisher=natalie |date=2011-10-21 |accessdate=2011-11-01}}</ref>、《[[MUSIC_STATION|MUSIC STATION]]》<ref>{{ja icon}}{{cite web|url=http://tower.jp/article/news/2011/10/25/n05 |title=〈Mステ〉10月28日放送回にAKB48、KinKi Kids、Perfumeら5組出演  |publisher=Tower |date=2011-10-25 |accessdate=2011-11-01}}</ref>、《[[魁！音樂排行榜|魁！音樂排行榜～EIGHT～]]》<ref>{{ja icon}}{{cite web|url=http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/NMSI94mVnxs/ |title=111026_AKB48_魁!音楽番付_Eight  |publisher=[[土豆網|土豆網]] |date=2011-10-26 |accessdate=2011-11-01}}</ref>、《{{Link-ja|1番SongSHOW|1番ソングSHOW}}》<ref>{{ja icon}}{{cite web|url=http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/-83tymeN2cE/ |title=111026_1番ソングSHOW！AKB48_Talk＋LIVE |publisher=[[土豆網|土豆網]] |date=2011-10-26 |accessdate=2011-11-01}}</ref> 和《[[HEY!HEY!HEY!MUSIC_CHAMP|HEY!HEY!HEY!MUSIC CHAMP]]》均有宣傳單曲<ref>{{ja icon}}{{cite web|url=http://www.toshiba.co.jp/regza/apps/ranking/tagdetail.php?id=8288 |title=AKB48: 風が吹いている 111017 HEY!HEY!HEY! |publisher=toshiba |date=2011-10-17 |accessdate=2011-11-01}}</ref>。

